rows.label: qst103908_msg0001
rows.name:
What? Whatwhatwhat?
Why you come back?

rows.label: qst103908_msg0002
rows.name:
Many strong monsters out there, so
Kebubu felt sure you not go, or if you
go then you get squishy-smashed...

rows.label: qst103908_msg0003
rows.name:
Ahhh! Don't angry, please!
Kebubu tell truth now!

rows.label: qst103908_msg0005
rows.name:
Sending fee is maybe teeny-weeny
bit higher than friends would
expect, so Kebubu not want to say.

rows.label: qst103908_msg0007
rows.name:
Courier business is tough
to run out of Superbia!

rows.label: qst103908_msg0008
rows.name:
Soldiers require many
bribes to smooth over
bureaucratic hold-ups.

rows.label: qst103908_msg0009
rows.name:
Then Kebubu feel bad about it, so
sometimes soothe feelings with
luxury spa package at hot spring.

rows.label: qst103908_msg0010
rows.name:
If sum is 82,166G, then...
66,554G get sent to Liberalitas.

rows.label: qst103908_msg0011
rows.name:
That whole truth!
Kebubu take no more than that.

rows.label: qst103908_msg0012
rows.name:
But do not know cost of
transport from Liberalitas
port to Iyasaki Village.

rows.label: qst103908_msg0013
rows.name:
If head to Rigitte Harbor in
Liberalitas, there is old man
courier there called Schuchit.

rows.label: qst103908_msg0014
rows.name: He can answer questions about monies.

rows.label: qst103908_msg0101
rows.name:
They say "Nopon small so must dock
at small jetty," even if ship is big.

rows.label: qst103908_msg0102
rows.name:
But they not say that to
Avaritia Trade Guild ship...
It very unfair!
